name: Failticity Online
description:
It's Failticity with a Twist, A Multiplayer Twist!

Reexperience Failticity all over again with new levels and new mechanics!

Features :

  • Free Roam - Mess Around with your Friends without a goal in mind!
  • Story Mode - New Story / Campaign with New Redesigned Levels with Multiplayer in-mind.  
  • Battle Mode - FPS Style Parkour Madness!
  • Builds for Windows 32 and 64 bit At the moment.
  • Cross-Platform Multiplayer!
  • and More on the way!

Are You a Twitch Streamer or Video Creator? Tweet at https://twitter.com/RainbowKappaTV to get a Copy for Free to Try-out!

Have Issues? - Tweet https://twitter.com/RainbowKappaTV or Email goldenethernetgames@gmail.com for Support!
